ian" lang="mk" hreflang="mk" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Македонски</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-mg mw-list-item"><a href="https://mg.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comenius" title="Comenius – Malagasy" lang="mg" hreflang="mg" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Malagasy</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-arz mw-list-item"><a href="https://arz.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%86_%D8%A2%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3_%D9%83%D9%88%D9%85%D9%8A%D9%86%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%B3" title="جان آموس كومينيوس – Egyptian Arabic" lang="arz" hreflang="arz" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>مصرى</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nl mw-list-item"><a href="https://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jan_Amos_Comenius" title="Jan Amos Comenius – Dutch" lang="nl" hreflang="nl" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Nederlands</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ja mw-list-item"><a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%A8%E3%83%8F%E3%83%8D%E3%82%B9%E3%83%BB%E3%82%A2%E3%83%A2%E3%82%B9%E3%83%BB%E3%82%B3%E3%83%A1%E3%83%8B%E3%82%A6%E3%82%B9" title="ヨハネス・アモス・コメニウス – Japanese" lang="ja" hreflang="ja" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>日本語</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-no mw-list-item"><a href="https://no.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johann_Amos_Comenius" title="Johann Amos Comenius – Norwegian Bokmål" lang="nb" hreflang="nb" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Norsk bokmål</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uz mw-list-item"><a href="https://uz.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yan_Amos_Komenskiy" title="Yan Amos Komenskiy – Uzbek" lang="uz" hreflang="uz" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Oʻzbekcha / ўзбекча</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ps mw-list-item"><a href="https://ps.wikipedia.org/wiki/%DB%8C%D8%A7%D9%86_%D8%A2%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3_%DA%A9%D9%85%DB%90%D9%86%D8%B3%DA%A9%D9%8A" title="یان آموس کمېنسکي – Pashto" lang="ps" hreflang="ps" class="interlanguage-link-targe